    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the \"balanced approach\" thing, but that's kinda a cop out lol. if u had to pick one to be the absolute priority to keep a country from collapsing, which would it be? like, is it more dangerous to have a massive debt or to have a population that's struggling with poverty and no support?",
